    FROM [Car] AS [x0]
    LEFT JOIN [Location] AS [x.CarLocation0] ON [x0].[CarLocationId] = [x.CarLocation0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Brand] AS [x.Brand0] ON [x0].[BrandId] = [x.Brand0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Model] AS [x.Model0] ON [x0].[ModelId] = [x.Model0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [FuelType] AS [x.FuelType0] ON [x0].[FuelTypeId] = [x.FuelType0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [TransmisionType] AS [x.TransmisionType0] ON [x0].[TransmisionTypeId] = [x.TransmisionType0].[Id]
    WHERE [x0].[IsDeleted] <> 1
) AS [t] ON [x.Booking].[CarId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
